summary: It’s Not A Game
title: It’s Not A Game
body:
What if there were Assassins and Templars in the Game of Thrones universe?

I know there’s already all sorts of things going on - politics, Faceless Men, crazy magic, etc.

But say that… oh… the Lannisters were also Templars, and Wintertown in the North, just outside of Winterfell, was the main base of operations for Assassins…

summary: That moment you realise that Cersei Lannister, the poster child for paranoia and cruel intentions, is a better person than...
title: That moment you realise that Cersei Lannister, the poster child for paranoia and cruel intentions, is a better person than Trump.
body: Fuck this Nazi Europe bullshit that is blatantly going on in the U.S, if I had dragons I’d burn down his administration and free those poor children back to their parents. Even Trump knows he’s gone too far but is too damn foolish to actually put a stop to it because in his tiny mind if he did that then people wouldn’t “respect” him.
